public class OsnMultiEOSendTrigger
extends oracle.jbo.rules.JboExpressionValidator

The validation trigger which when evaluated will call OAEntityImpl.secondaryEOSentToOSN via an EL expression. The primary use case is that this trigger will be executed when an afterCommit occurs on a class that is participating in a multi-EO scenario.
